    "However, the utilization of transfer learning and reinforcement learning in CLMs entails additional machine learning steps, which can pose challenges in terms of speed and seamless integration within the design-make-test-analysis cycle in medicinal chemistry [14] [15] [16].",
    "Furthermore, transfer learning can be particularly challenging when applied to a single fine-tuning molecule 7, 17.",
